THIS HOME QUALIFIES FOR MULTIPLE DOWN PAYMENT ASSISTANCE GRANTS AND PROGRAMS CALL NOW TO FIND OUT MORE! 
Welcome home! This charming two level home nestled in the quite Hyde Grove neighborhood has SO much to love and MORE. Featuring a double lot, just under an acre of cleared land, and fully fenced back yard, you're sure to find all the space you could ever need for outdoor activities and family fun! The home itself is an eclectic and comfy layout, featuring a main living room with eat in space kitchen, a second level balcony, 5 bedrooms, and 2 full bathrooms. It's truly a MUST SEE. 
NEW ROOF* with 15 year warranty 
NEW HVAC*
